The paper also discusses the use of betweenness centrality and diversity measures in analyzing journal citation networks, which are relevant to the fields of social networks (cs.SI) and software engineering (cs.SD). Finally, the paper discusses the difficulty in operationalizing interdisciplinarity, which is a topic relevant to the field of cybernetics (cs.CY).
